snippet.title: EVE: War of Ascension Trailer
snippet.description:
For the first time ever, the hit EVE Online world is coming to mobile as EVE: War of Ascension. 

Play EVE: War of Ascension on mobile devices!

The game is a space-based, persistent world massively multiplayer online role-playing game. Pick a Corporation and work together to create empires. There are endless ways to embark on your personal sci-fi adventure to domination!

Don't forget to SUBSCRIBE ► http://kon.gg/2GYLmTu
